宣传，阻碍灌木丛清理、住宅消防安全检查，还限制了重大灾害中重型设备的调用。更多资讯请下载央视新闻客户端"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-a9ff27977a9329dcd10dfffeafac7345_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "384 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/9206744683"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIst7k56ueuNQDEAMaCTExMjgxNzkxNSDet4G8BjAAOMUDQAVyCjkyMDY3NDQ2ODN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1736486501.89023", "card_id": "Q_9132536525", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 64}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "拳头公布《英雄联盟》新英雄「梅尔」核心技能将能够「反弹」所有技能，该技能将给游戏环境带来哪些影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "新英雄梅尔的新技能玩法——反弹"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-a258f3d388a6dfa413282d8d5bf1888f_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "242 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/9132536525"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIst7k56ueuNQDEAMaCTExMjgwMzEwNCC+jP27BjAAOE5ABnIKOTEzMjUzNjUyNXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1736486501.89414", "card_id": "Q_9180437035", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 45}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待鸿蒙原生版微信在 1 月 9 日正式上架，实际体验如何？与普通版微信有哪些差异？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "《科创板日报》9 日讯，鸿蒙原生版微信今日上架鸿蒙应用市场，支持视频号、折叠消息转发、群红包、转账、小程序等功能，与普通版微信功能基本相同。目前，微信、支付宝、抖音、京东、淘宝、美团、 WPS Office 等均已上架，原生鸿蒙生态版图的最后一块 TOP 应用完成。(记者黄心怡）"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-00a1d01c7e468b783296749547aeb825_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "228 万热度", "font_color": "", "